# erc-colorize

Per user colorization of whole message

## Installation

Install the ELPA package from MELPA with <kbd>M-x</kbd>
`package-install` <kbd>RET</kbd> `erc-colorize` or put
`erc-colorize.el` in you load path and require it somewhere in your
`.emacs`.

Activate the ERC module with:
```lisp
(erc-colorize-mode 1)
```

## Settings

The faces used to colorize messages are stored in
`erc-colorize-faces`.
